# The Tailwind standalone binary is the only build dependency and is ~46 MB.
# It is NOT committed — run `tools/fetch-tailwind.sh` to fetch the pinned version.
# The built CSS (assets/css/output.css) IS committed, so the site runs on clone
# with no build step; you only need the binary to rebuild the CSS.
/tools/tailwindcss
